title: Imaan Hammam
summary:
Imaan Hammam (born 5 October 1996) is a Moroccan model. As of 2020, she has appeared on the cover of Vogue 18 times, four times on the American edition of Vogue.
She currently ranks on models.com's "Industry Icons" and was ranked on its "Top Sexiest Models" lists. As of 2021, she has appeared on The Big Four covers of Vogue.
